<font color="#D900D9">(GLASS SHATTERS)</font>

42:13.240 --> 42:15.325
<font color="#D900D9">(GRUNTING)</font>

42:20.622 --> 42:22.624
<font color="#D900D9">(SNIFFS)</font>

42:25.586 --> 42:26.920
<font color="#D900D9">(GROANS)</font>

42:27.880 --> 42:29.882
<font color="#D900D9">(SCREAMS THEN SOBBING)</font>

42:31.050 --> 42:32.926
<font color="#808080">LITA:</font>
No.

42:33.093 --> 42:34.636
Please.

42:38.057 --> 42:39.516
No.

42:41.393 --> 42:43.395
<font color="#D900D9">(GROANING)</font>

42:45.439 --> 42:47.983
<font color="#D900D9">(KNOCKING ON DOOR)</font>

42:57.076 --> 42:58.744
That's probably her now.

43:01.747 --> 43:04.208
Hey, sweetheart.
How's it going?

43:04.374 --> 43:05.876
<font color="#808080">ANGELA:</font>
It's been an interesting night.

43:06.043 --> 43:09.797
<font color="#808080">JASON:</font> Yeah. I saw the power outage
and I thought I'd bring you some candles.

43:10.214 --> 43:13.592
