Yeah, I'm fine. Thanks, honey.

43:13.759 --> 43:16.512
Mose, can you light some of these for me?<font color="#808080">
MOSE:</font> Sure.

43:16.678 --> 43:19.348
<font color="#808080">JASON:</font>
So, what's going on?

43:20.099 --> 43:23.143
I've got a fugitive who's being picked up
by the marshals...

43:23.310 --> 43:25.354
