Heh. Yeah, probably is.

43:28.649 --> 43:30.484
<font color="#808080">JASON:</font> You hungry?<font color="#808080">
ANGELA:</font> Starving.

43:30.651 --> 43:34.029
<font color="#808080">JASON:</font> Why don't call your deputies
and come home for a sandwich?

43:34.196 --> 43:37.699
I can't reach them
and besides, I should really stay here.

43:37.866 --> 43:41.745
Those guys aren't going anywhere.
Take some time for yourself, you know?

43:41.912 --> 43:44.414
Even the sheriff is entitled
to a lunch break.

43:44.581 --> 43:46.792
<font color="#808080">ANGELA:</font> Jason.<font color="#808080">
JASON:</font> All right.

43:46.959 --> 43:49.878
I'll go fix some sandwiches
and I'll be back in a bit.

43:50.045 --> 43:52.297
Last supper.

43:54.299 --> 43:56.301
What's his problem?

43:56.468 --> 43:58.720
Who is that guy?
Don't ask.

43:59.596 --> 44:01.557
Okay. See you soon.

44:01.723 --> 44:03.517
<font color="#808080">ANGELA:</font>
See you later.

44:06.395 --> 44:08.397
<font color="#D900D9">(DOOR CLOSES)</font>

44:09.898 --> 44:11.233
<font color="#808080">GUS:</font> <i>
Help!</i>

44:11.400 --> 44:13.360
Somebody help!

44:13.527 --> 44:17.239
