44:22.035 --> 44:23.662
<font color="#D900D9">(SCREAMING)</font>

44:24.079 --> 44:25.622
Somebody help!

44:28.417 --> 44:29.918
Somebody!

44:30.085 --> 44:31.503
Help!

44:32.421 --> 44:34.339
Help me!

44:35.007 --> 44:37.885
Let me go, you crazy fuck.

44:38.385 --> 44:40.596
<font color="#D900D9">(ONE EYE, SAW TOOTH
& THREE FINGER LAUGHING)</font>

44:40.762 --> 44:42.514
What are you doing?

44:43.307 --> 44:44.391
No.

44:44.558 --> 44:46.435
No. No.

44:46.935 --> 44:48.604
Please, no, no.

44:48.770 --> 44:49.813
<font color="#D900D9">(SCREAMING)</font>

45:16.423 --> 45:18.091
Fifty cents.

45:18.258 --> 45:21.053
Buck.
Uh... Call.

45:21.220 --> 45:23.180
<font color="#D900D9">(HORN HONKING)</font>

45:26.391 --> 45:27.851
<font color="#808080">MOSE:</font>
Who are they?

45:28.018 --> 45:30.938
I don't know.
I never seen the truck before.

45:39.821 --> 45:41.281
<font color="#808080">MAYNARD:</font>
I told you.

45:41.740 --> 45:44.826
It's my boys. They're here to get me.

45:46.161 --> 45:48.830
<font color="#D900D9">(GRUNTING)</font>

45:48.997 --> 45:50.290
Shit.

45:55.003 --> 45:57.965
Help!
That's Gus.

45:58.131 --> 46:00.342
<font color="#D900D9">(GUS SCREAMING)</font>

46:00.509 --> 46:03.470
Somebody, please!

46:03.637 --> 46:07.099
Help!

46:09.643 --> 46:11.186
<font color="#D900D9">(SCREAMING)</font>

46:13.188 --> 46:14.940
<font color="#D900D9">(THREE FINGER CACKLING)</font>

46:20.821 --> 46:24.658
Oh, God. We gotta get him out
of the middle of the road.

46:24.825 --> 46:25.826
<font color="#D900D9">(RETCHES AND COUGHS)</font>

46:25.993 --> 46:28.870
Oh, I can't. I can't.

46:29.705 --> 46:31.456
Give me a hand.

46:31.623 --> 46:33.625
<font color="#D900D9">(JULIAN VOMITING)</font>

46:39.214 --> 46:41.216
<font color="#D900D9">(CHUCKLES)</font>

46:45.887 --> 46:48.390
One down, huh, sheriff?

46:48.557 --> 46:51.893
You're not going anywhere
and you're gonna pay for this.

46:52.394 --> 46:54.563
You hear me, you bastard?

46:54.730 --> 46:56.565
<font color="#808080">MOSE:</font>
What are we gonna do?

46:56.732 --> 47:00.235
<font color="#D900D9">(MAYNARD WHISTLING)</font>

47:01.361 --> 47:02.529
<font color="#808080">ANGELA:</font>
Get out.

47:02.696 --> 47:04.573
I need to find Cruz.<font color="#808080">
JULIAN:</font> And Lita.

47:04.740 --> 47:06.366
<font color="#808080">ANGELA:</font>
Listen to me.

47:08.535 --> 47:10.412
You're all deputized.

47:11.413 --> 47:14.416
If you help me, it will go a long way
in my report to the court.

47:14.583 --> 47:17.502
But I wanna go after my girlfriend.
No, we all stay here.

47:17.669 --> 47:19.421
We hold out until help arrives.

47:20.255 --> 47:22.424
Mose, you watch the front door.

47:22.591 --> 47:24.301
You two, cover the windows.

47:24.760 --> 47:25.761
<font color="#D900D9">(SHOTGUN COCKING)</font>

47:26.636 --> 47:30.432
They want us to split up. It makes it
easier for them to kill us that way.

47:30.599 --> 47:34.603
So we should stick together,
here until dawn. Now, get to your stations.

47:35.354 --> 47:37.814
We need to call for help.
Lines are dead. Cell too.

47:37.981 --> 47:42.652
Uh, sheriff, uh, Lee has a short-wave radio in
the back of his thrift store. I've seen it.

47:42.819 --> 47:45.906
We need power to operate it.
Lee has a generator. Good thinking.

47:46.073 --> 47:48.450
Listen, I'm gonna go across
the street to the store.

47:48.617 --> 47:50.952
I'm gonna fire up the shortwave
and call for help.

47:51.119 --> 47:52.704
I'll go with you.
No, no, no.

47:52.871 --> 47:54.790
You stay
and make sure they don't get in.

47:54.956 --> 47:58.001
Not a bright idea there, sheriff.

47:58.168 --> 48:01.463
Split up and die, remember?
He's right.

48:01.630 --> 48:03.340
<font color="#808080">ANGELA:</font>
I will not risk your lives.

48:03.507 --> 48:06.009
This is my job.
Now, cover me when I'm on the street.

48:48.802 --> 48:49.970
Okay.

48:50.137 --> 48:52.055
Okay, where are you?

48:52.222 --> 48:54.015
Okay, come on.

48:54.641 --> 48:58.270
Where are you? Where are you?
Where are you?

48:59.855 --> 49:01.189
Yes.

49:07.904 --> 49:09.573
<font color="#D900D9">(GRUNTS)</font>

49:17.706 --> 49:19.207
<font color="#D900D9">(GRUNTS)</font>

49:20.917 --> 49:22.502
Okay.

49:23.712 --> 49:25.213
Okay.

49:31.386 --> 49:32.888
Okay.

49:33.054 --> 49:35.932
Gas.

49:37.893 --> 49:39.478
Yeah.

49:44.900 --> 49:46.443
Okay.

49:53.742 --> 49:56.286
<font color="#D900D9">(THREE FINGER CACKLING)</font>

50:03.919 --> 50:07.380
We should go help her.
Nope. I gave my word I'd stay here.

50:07.547 --> 50:09.424
I'll go.
Give it a minute.

50:09.591 --> 50:12.344
Just... If we hear another shot, we'll go.
But we don't...

50:12.511 --> 50:14.763
We don't know this woman.
She's not Cruz or Lita.

50:14.930 --> 50:18.266
We should be going after them. Just wait.
Let's go find the girls.

50:18.433 --> 50:22.062
If you leave, they'll throw the book at you.
Wait a few minutes, see if she comes.

50:22.229 --> 50:25.649
If she does, we'll tell her
we're both going. All right.

50:25.815 --> 50:27.776
Ten minutes.

50:36.618 --> 50:38.119
<font color="#D900D9">(SIGHS)</font>

50:49.798 --> 50:51.591
<font color="#D900D9">(GENERATOR SPUTTERS)</font>

50:52.092 --> 50:53.468
<font color="#D900D9">(GENERATOR STARTS)</font>

50:58.265 --> 51:00.267
<font color="#D900D9">(STATIC CRACKLING)</font>

51:01.476 --> 51:04.062
This is Sheriff Carter of Fairlake
declaring emergency.

51:04.229 --> 51:06.439
<font color="#D900D9">(OVER RADIO)</font> <i>
Is anyone out there? Over.</i>

51:06.606 --> 51:08.608
<font color="#D900D9">(REGGAE MUSIC
PLAYING OVER SPEAKERS)</font>

51:11.570 --> 51:14.614
<i>Sheriff Carter of Fair/ake, West Virginia
declaring an emergency.</i>

51:14.781 --> 51:17.325
Can anyone hear me? Over.

51:17.492 --> 51:20.453
<i>Yup, I hear you, sheriff.</i>

51:20.787 --> 51:22.998
What's your name and where are you?

51:23.665 --> 51:26.376
Uh, Teddy Tabet.
I'm in Dixville Notch, New Hampshire.

51:26.543 --> 51:29.296
<i>Okay, listen to me carefully, Teddy.</i>

51:29.462 --> 51:32.757
<i>I need you to call the Virginia
State Police in Moundsville.</i>

51:32.924 --> 51:36.553
Have them send every available officer
to Fairlake right away.

51:36.720 --> 51:38.096
It's an emergency.

51:38.722 --> 51:40.181
What's going on down there?

51:40.348 --> 51:43.685
<i>The town is under siege by three hillbillies.
They're trying to break...</i>

51:43.852 --> 51:47.689
<i>...one of their relatives out of jail.
They've already killed one person already.</i>

51:48.690 --> 51:51.484
Did you say Fairlake, West Virginia?

51:51.651 --> 51:53.862
Yes, that's right.
And we have no phone service.

51:54.029 --> 51:57.198
So I need you to call the state police
right away. Can you do that?

51:57.365 --> 51:59.534
<i>Okay, okay. One minute.</i>

52:01.286 --> 52:03.288
<font color="#D900D9">(TYPING ON KEYBOARD)</font>

52:05.165 --> 52:07.250
<font color="#D900D9">(LAUGHING)</font>

52:09.294 --> 52:10.378
Are you stoned?

52:11.254 --> 52:12.339
What?

52:13.214 --> 52:16.009
Are you stoned or do you just think
I'm stupid?

52:16.176 --> 52:19.054
What are you talking about, Teddy?
I need your help.

52:19.220 --> 52:21.389
<i>Tonight's the Mountain Man Festival,
right?</i>

52:21.556 --> 52:24.601
You think it would be funny
to scramble the entire state police...

52:24.768 --> 52:26.728
...because you convinced
some dork to call?

52:26.895 --> 52:28.104
This is real.

52:28.271 --> 52:30.440
I am the sheriff and I need your help.

52:30.607 --> 52:31.775
This is serious, Teddy.

52:31.941 --> 52:35.320
<i>Hey, listen, it's a felony
to file a fake police report, okay?</i>

52:35.487 --> 52:38.823
I'm not stupid. We here in Dixville Notch
are a pretty savvy bunch.

52:38.990 --> 52:40.825
You can't pull the wool over my eyes.

52:40.992 --> 52:43.328
So, uh, yeah, heh,
have a good night, officer.

52:43.495 --> 52:46.373
Wait, wait, wait. Please, listen, Teddy,
you gotta believe me.

52:46.539 --> 52:48.249
This is a matter of life and death.

52:54.172 --> 52:55.256
<font color="#D900D9">(SCREAMS)</font>

52:55.757 --> 52:57.425
Shit.
What was that?

52:57.592 --> 52:58.843
<i>Somebody dying.</i>

52:59.010 --> 53:02.222
You believe me now, asshole?
Just call the police.

53:08.520 --> 53:11.272
<font color="#D900D9">(GENERATOR POWERS DOWN)</font>

53:12.107 --> 53:15.110
<font color="#808080">MOSE:</font> I think I got one of them.<font color="#808080">
BILLY:</font> Shit, shit.

53:15.652 --> 53:18.071
You idiot. What if that was the sheriff?

53:20.615 --> 53:22.575
<font color="#D900D9">(SCREAMING)</font>

53:27.664 --> 53:29.290
Are you hurt?

53:30.583 --> 53:33.044
Oh, my God. Is that Gus?

53:33.211 --> 53:34.295
Is that Gus?

53:34.462 --> 53:36.047
Come inside.

53:37.507 --> 53:39.134
<font color="#808080">LITA:</font>
Oh, my God.

53:41.136 --> 53:42.137
<font color="#808080">BILLY:</font>
Shh, Shh, shh.

53:42.303 --> 53:45.390
All right, okay.
You're all right. You're all right.

53:49.352 --> 53:51.146
<font color="#808080">ANGELA:</font>
Julian, let me in.

53:52.814 --> 53:56.359
What happened?
This drunk nearly killed my friend.

53:56.526 --> 53:57.902
I'm sorry. I'm so sorry.

53:58.069 --> 54:00.655
He has no business carrying a gun.
It was an accident!

54:00.822 --> 54:03.825
I should beat this shit out of you!
Hey, calm down. Calm down.

54:03.992 --> 54:06.745
I said, calm down.

54:09.789 --> 54:11.291
Were you hit?
No.

54:11.458 --> 54:12.917
Okay. Have you seen Cruz?

54:13.084 --> 54:14.836
Were you with her?

54:15.295 --> 54:17.422
She left before Julian.

54:17.589 --> 54:19.966
<font color="#808080">MAYNARD:</font>
She's dead, lover boy.

54:21.259 --> 54:24.095
Probably being digested right now.

54:24.721 --> 54:27.807
My boys have a taste for flesh...

54:28.975 --> 54:30.769
...especially cute little blonds.

54:30.935 --> 54:33.938
Will you shut the fuck up?

54:34.689 --> 54:37.901
If anything happened to her,
I'm gonna fucking kill you.

54:42.697 --> 54:44.199
<font color="#D900D9">(SHOTGUN COCKS)</font>

54:47.702 --> 54:49.537
Let me go...

54:49.704 --> 54:53.583
...and maybe the rest of them
will live to see the dawn.

54:53.750 --> 54:55.335
You're not getting out of there.

54:55.502 --> 54:58.379
There's four of you and one of her.

54:58.546 --> 55:00.548
Think how much you wanna live.

55:00.715 --> 55:04.177
You're out of your mind if you think
any one of us is gonna let you out.

55:04.886 --> 55:06.554
Suit yourselves.

55:08.973 --> 55:12.060
Did you reach anybody
on the short wave?

55:12.227 --> 55:14.395
Yes.
Great. That means help is coming.

55:14.562 --> 55:16.064
I don't know.
What do you mean?

55:16.231 --> 55:19.734
The dumb shit on the other line,
I don't think he believed me.

55:19.943 --> 55:22.487
I'm going to look for Cruz.
Hey, I told you, no.

55:22.654 --> 55:25.990
Well, then you better lock me back up.<font color="#808080">
ANGELA:</font> What?

55:26.157 --> 55:27.575
All right, I may be a fuck up.

55:27.742 --> 55:32.580
I'm irresponsible, I'm unreliable and I'm
definitely juvenile, but I am loyal.

55:33.373 --> 55:35.083
I love Cruz.

55:35.750 --> 55:38.586
I love her more than anything
I've ever loved in my life...

55:38.753 --> 55:41.798
...and I'm not gonna sit in here
while she's out there on her own.

55:41.965 --> 55:44.259
I couldn't live with myself if I did that.

55:44.425 --> 55:48.429
So either lock me up or let me go.

55:50.431 --> 55:53.852
Here, you're gonna need this.
Thank you.

55:55.144 --> 55:58.106
I'm going with you.
All right.

56:00.692 --> 56:02.277
You gonna be all right?

56:03.027 --> 56:04.529
Be careful.

56:05.280 --> 56:06.823
We Will.

56:15.540 --> 56:18.251
We'll look around here,
see if we can find her.

56:18.668 --> 56:21.129
All right. Keep your eyes open.

56:27.468 --> 56:29.220
Cruz.

56:31.180 --> 56:32.682
Cruz, it's Billy.

56:32.849 --> 56:34.559
Come out.

56:37.979 --> 56:40.982
If Cruz knows what's up,
she'll be hiding and won't come out.

56:41.149 --> 56:42.609
Yeah.

56:44.819 --> 56:46.821
I hope that's the case.

56:59.334 --> 57:02.921
Mister?
Call me Mose.

57:03.212 --> 57:04.547
<font color="#D900D9">(SOBBING)</font>

57:06.007 --> 57:08.009
Why are they doing this?

57:08.509 --> 57:10.511
They wanna break him out, I suppose.

57:10.678 --> 57:13.348
But killing innocent people?

57:14.557 --> 57:16.601
Why kill Gus?

57:16.768 --> 57:19.896
He had nothing to do
with keeping that old guy locked up.

57:20.063 --> 57:23.858
I get the feeling that killing ain't
too much of a stretch for this bunch.

57:28.029 --> 57:29.614
What if no help comes?

57:30.365 --> 57:32.200
It will. Don't worry.

57:35.036 --> 57:37.372
And Billy and Julian?

57:37.872 --> 57:39.624
They'll find your friend...

57:39.791 --> 57:41.542
...and then they'll be back.

57:48.299 --> 57:49.968
Cruz!

57:50.343 --> 57:52.679
Are you out there?

57:53.054 --> 57:56.349
Where the hell could she be?
I don't know, man.

57:58.101 --> 57:59.227
<font color="#D900D9">(THREE FINGER CACKLING)</font>

57:59.394 --> 58:00.395
Jesus Christ.

58:00.561 --> 58:02.438
What the hell was that?

58:03.564 --> 58:05.358
Move, Billy.

58:07.235 --> 58:09.195
<font color="#D900D9">(MEN CACKLING)</font>

58:09.362 --> 58:11.698
Shit. Shit.

58:12.699 --> 58:15.076
We gotta get out of the street.
We're sitting ducks.

58:15.243 --> 58:16.911
There.

58:34.595 --> 58:37.265
Oh, shit. Cruz.

58:37.890 --> 58:39.726
Oh, my God, baby.

58:39.892 --> 58:42.353
Oh, my God.

58:42.520 --> 58:43.771
Oh, Cruz.

58:43.938 --> 58:46.774
What kind of fucking animals are they?

58:46.941 --> 58:48.735
<font color="#808080">JULIAN:</font>
There's nothing we can do for her now.

58:48.901 --> 58:50.069
I'm taking her back.

58:50.236 --> 58:53.239
I'm not gonna leave her here
like some piece of trash.

58:54.782 --> 58:56.451
Oh, Jesus.

58:56.617 --> 58:58.619
<font color="#D900D9">(THREE FINGER CACKLING)</font>

59:00.121 --> 59:01.456
Son of a bitch.

59:02.248 --> 59:03.541
<font color="#808080">JULIAN:</font>
Billy!

59:10.381 --> 59:11.924
<font color="#D900D9">(JULIAN GRUNTS)</font>

59:26.272 --> 59:27.648
<font color="#D900D9">(BOTH GRUNTING)</font>

59:35.990 --> 59:39.619
<font color="#D900D9">(COUGHING)</font>

59:49.128 --> 59:50.880
<font color="#D900D9">(PANTING)</font>

01:00:05.770 --> 01:00:08.523
Julian.

01:00:08.689 --> 01:00:09.732
Wake up!

01:00:09.899 --> 01:00:11.734
<font color="#D900D9">(COUGHS)</font>

01:00:11.901 --> 01:00:13.569
Fuck.
Shit.

01:00:13.736 --> 01:00:15.279
Oh, God, Bi...

01:00:15.446 --> 01:00:17.281
Billy, what's going on?
I can't move.

01:00:17.448 --> 01:00:19.826
I can't move.
You gotta get out of that chain, man.

01:00:19.992 --> 01:00:21.452
Chain?

01:00:21.828 --> 01:00:22.870
Can you get out?

01:00:23.037 --> 01:00:24.539
<font color="#808080">JULIAN:</font>
Shit.

01:00:25.706 --> 01:00:27.708
Fuck. No. Just... No.

01:00:27.875 --> 01:00:29.877
Fuck.
No, there's...

01:00:30.044 --> 01:00:32.797
We gotta call for help. All right?

01:00:33.214 --> 01:00:34.814
Help!

01:00:40.304 --> 01:00:42.390
<font color="#808080">BILLY:</font> Help us, anybody!<font color="#808080">
JULIAN:</font> Help!

01:00:42.557 --> 01:00:45.309
<font color="#808080">BILLY:</font> Anybody!
Help!

01:00:45.476 --> 01:00:46.477
Fuck.

01:00:46.644 --> 01:00:47.895
<font color="#D900D9">(THREE FINGER CACKLING)</font>

01:00:48.062 --> 01:00:50.731
Where is he? Where is he?

01:00:51.232 --> 01:00:52.400
Where is he?

01:00:52.567 --> 01:00:55.153
<font color="#D900D9">(ENGINE STARTS)</font>

01:00:55.319 --> 01:00:57.029
